ActCustoms Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Designated Provisions (Customs) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the DESIGNATED PROVISIONS (CUSTOMS) REGULATIONS in order to allow the Canada Border Services Agency to pre-screen all travellers destined for Canada in order to provide board/no-board information to commercial air carriers concerning the passengers expected to be on board commercial flights prior to a flight's departure for Canada in the context of the Interactive Advance Passenger Information initiative.
